{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/posts/Django/languages","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"c94aa553-2767-533b-9d22-57ab315339ff","html":"<h2 id=\"용어-정리\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%9A%A9%EC%96%B4-%EC%A0%95%EB%A6%AC\" aria-label=\"용어 정리 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>용어 정리</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>국제화(i18n, internationalization): 개발자가 지역화 지원을 위해 소프트웨어적으로 준비하는 것</li>\n<li>지역화(l8n, localization): 번역가가 번역하고 지역 형식에 맞게 변환하는 것</li>\n<li>로케일 이름: ko<em>KR은 대한민국 한국어이고 ko</em>KP는 북한 한국어 의미로 “언어_국가” 형식이다.</li>\n<li>언어 코드: 브라우저가 HTTP 헤더 Accept-Language로 보내는 값으로 “언어-국가” 형식이며 ko-kr 같이 쓰는데 모두 소문자로 되어 있다. Django 설정 파일에서 쓰이는 값이다.</li>\n<li>.po 파일: 번역가가 직접 번역하는 메시지 파일이다.</li>\n<li>.mo 파일: Django가 인식할 수 있도록 개발자가.po 번역 메시지 파일을 컴파일해 만든 파일이다.</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"set-up\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#set-up\" aria-label=\"set up permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Set up</h1>\n<h3 id=\"django-전역-설정\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#django-%EC%A0%84%EC%97%AD-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95\" aria-label=\"django 전역 설정 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Django 전역 설정</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>SessionMiddleware와 CommonMiddleware 사이에 LocaleMiddleware를 추가한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\">MIDDLEWARE <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">'django.middleware.security.SecurityMiddleware'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">'django.contrib.sessions.middleware.SessionMiddleware'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">'django.middleware.locale.LocaleMiddleware'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token comment\"># here</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">'django.middleware.common.CommonMiddleware'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">'django.middleware.csrf.CsrfViewMiddleware'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">'django.contrib.auth.middleware.AuthenticationMiddleware'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">'django.contrib.messages.middleware.MessageMiddleware'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">'django.middleware.clickjacking.XFrameOptionsMiddleware'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>settings.py 파일에서 다음 내용을 수정한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\">LANGUAGE_CODE <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'ko-KR'</span></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>settings.py 파일에서 상단에 다음과 같이 import문을 추가하고, 프로젝트에서 지원할 다국어 언어값을 설정한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> django<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>utils<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>translation <span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> ugettext_lazy <span class=\"token keyword\">as</span> _\n\nLANGUAGES <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>  <span class=\"token comment\"># Available languages</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'ko'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> _<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'Korean'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'en'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> _<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'English'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'ch'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> _<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'Chinese'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'ja'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> _<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'Japanese'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>settings.py 파일에서 번역 파일이 들어있는 locale 디렉토리를 지정하고 실제로 디렉토리를 생성한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\">LOCALE_PATHS <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n    os<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>path<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>join<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>BASE_DIR<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'locale'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h1 id=\"번역-파일-만들기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%B2%88%EC%97%AD-%ED%8C%8C%EC%9D%BC-%EB%A7%8C%EB%93%A4%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"번역 파일 만들기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>번역 파일 만들기</h1>\n<h3 id=\"modelspy-예시\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#modelspy-%EC%98%88%EC%8B%9C\" aria-label=\"modelspy 예시 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>models.py 예시</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> django<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>utils<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>translation <span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> ugettext_lazy <span class=\"token keyword\">as</span> _\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Post</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>models<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>Model<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    STATUS_CHOICES <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'draft'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> _<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'Draft'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'published'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> _<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'Published'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n    title <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> models<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>CharField<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>_<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'Title'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> max_length<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token number\">250</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"templatehtml-예시\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#templatehtml-%EC%98%88%EC%8B%9C\" aria-label=\"templatehtml 예시 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>template.html 예시</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>a</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">href</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>{% url 'blog:post_index' %}<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>{{ _('Blog') }}<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>a</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"번역-메시지-파일-생성\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%B2%88%EC%97%AD-%EB%A9%94%EC%8B%9C%EC%A7%80-%ED%8C%8C%EC%9D%BC-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1\" aria-label=\"번역 메시지 파일 생성 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>번역 메시지 파일 생성</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>아래 명령어로 전체 메시지 파일을 만들 수 있다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"vim\"><pre class=\"language-vim\"><code class=\"language-vim\"><span class=\"token keyword\">python</span> manage<span class=\"token operator\">.</span><span class=\"token keyword\">py</span> makemessage <span class=\"token operator\">-</span>a</code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>잘 되지 않으면 언어별로 생성한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"vim\"><pre class=\"language-vim\"><code class=\"language-vim\"><span class=\"token keyword\">python</span> manage<span class=\"token operator\">.</span><span class=\"token keyword\">py</span> makemessages <span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token keyword\">l</span> ko\n<span class=\"token keyword\">python</span> manage<span class=\"token operator\">.</span><span class=\"token keyword\">py</span> makemessages <span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token keyword\">l</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">en</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">python</span> manage<span class=\"token operator\">.</span><span class=\"token keyword\">py</span> makemessages <span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token keyword\">l</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">ch</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">python</span> manage<span class=\"token operator\">.</span><span class=\"token keyword\">py</span> makemessages <span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token keyword\">l</span> ja</code></pre></div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"메시지-파일-컴파일\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%A9%94%EC%8B%9C%EC%A7%80-%ED%8C%8C%EC%9D%BC-%EC%BB%B4%ED%8C%8C%EC%9D%BC\" aria-label=\"메시지 파일 컴파일 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>메시지 파일 컴파일</h3>\n<p>(컴파일 후에는 Django 서버를 재기동해야 메시지 번역 결과가 반영된다.)</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"vim\"><pre class=\"language-vim\"><code class=\"language-vim\"><span class=\"token keyword\">python</span> manage<span class=\"token operator\">.</span><span class=\"token keyword\">py</span> compilemessages</code></pre></div>\n<h1 id=\"fuzzy-플래그\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#fuzzy-%ED%94%8C%EB%9E%98%EA%B7%B8\" aria-label=\"fuzzy 플래그 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>fuzzy 플래그</h1>\n<p>.po 메시지 파일에 주석으로 #, fuzzy 표시가 있으면 해당 문자열은 번역되지 않는다. 따라서 번역 문자열 상단에 주석으로 #, fuzzy 표시가 있으면 해당 부분의 주석을 삭제한다.</p>\n<h1 id=\"macos에서-gettext-설치\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#macos%EC%97%90%EC%84%9C-gettext-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98\" aria-label=\"macos에서 gettext 설치 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>MacOS에서 gettext 설치</h1>\n<p>아래와 같이 gettext 프로그램이 설치되어 있지 않을 경우 이를 설치해야 한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"vim\"><pre class=\"language-vim\"><code class=\"language-vim\"><span class=\"token keyword\">python</span> manage<span class=\"token operator\">.</span><span class=\"token keyword\">py</span> makemessages\nCommandError<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> Can'<span class=\"token keyword\">t</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">find</span> xgettext<span class=\"token operator\">.</span> Make sure you have GNU gettext tools <span class=\"token number\">0.15</span> or newer installed<span class=\"token operator\">.</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>아래와 같이 brew로 gettext를 설치한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"vim\"><pre class=\"language-vim\"><code class=\"language-vim\">brew install gettext\nbrew link gettext <span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span>force</code></pre></div>\n<p>단순히 설치만 하고 링크하지 않으면 명령행에서 실행할 수가 없다.</p>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/Django/languages","tagSlugs":["/tag/django-languages/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2020-11-02","description":"django locations 다국어 적용하기","tags":["django-languages"],"title":"Django 다국어 적용하기","socialImage":""}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/posts/Django/languages"}}}